#- Chapter 3: Belthazor19's Shitstorm

Before the BK shitstorm, we encountered a pair of petty griefers named futhermucker and mrpotatoz.Bethazor19, being the fighting instigator he is, after Eslenti's failure, came
#- to Orion to help with them. He pearled futhermucker and then started to build up wealth in Orion. He was griefed a few times so he had a hissy fit and rage quit. To do this, he admitted to hacking on /r/Civcraft and was promptly banned. Him and a few
#- others from the "Blackknights" began attacking Orion. The only one of these criminals you will recognize is SuperBuilder229, whom bettered himself and rejoined society only for a brief moment before he was sucked into the soul crushing vortex of Kappi.
#- Chapter 4: Peacetime then Butter Brigade Incidents

We had a short period of peace, and while in this time some players joined us including ChasHOlsen and many more. I won't go into full detail, as this thread covers the main event. Before that event, the
#-  Orion 101 was deconstructed and stolen, causing a bit of a panic. I managed to pearl one of the griefers (Mariaha) only to get her broken out of a 4 layer vault we had.
#- Chapter 5: Present and the Future

As of now, we have withstanded numerous attacks from all kinds of people. Some more recent criminals include the Poser Brigade among others.

We will continue to defend ourselves to
#- the point of no return. No matter who attacks us or how numerous they are, we will not falter. We are Orion. We are Stronk.
#- 